If you want any advice on playing this system in ACBL-land, best to contact either Dianas or nfmfl, who have played good level Pairs tournaments in the USA using this system.  Maybe some others have navigated the ACBL waters as well, but I'm not aware.

Diana and David prepared a special version of the system that DID definitely comply with the way ACBL insisted on having things (and did pretty well with it, as I recall).|
